Package edu.ncsu.csc216.androtech.model.repair_center

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComDroid
    Class used to represent a service droid of type communication, which is a member of the abstract TechDroids class
    ComDroidTest
    Method used to test the ComDroid class for our program through various testing strategies
    ExpertDroid
    Class used to represent a service droid of both type communications and virtual reality, which is a member of the abstract TechDroids class
    ExpertDroidTest
    Method used to test the ExpertDroid class for our program through various strategies
    RepairCenter
    Class representing an array list of tech droids that will be used to repair the various devices.
    RepairCenterTest
    Method used to test the RepairCenter class for our program through various strategies
    TechDroid
    Abstract class representing the methods/data members of a tech-droid, which is use to repair communication or virtual reality devices
    TechDroidTest
    Method used to test the TechDroid class for our program through various strategies
    VRDroid
    Class used to represent a service droid of type virtual reality, which is a member of the abstract TechDroids class
    VRDroidTest
    Method used to test the V class for our program through various testing strategies
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DroidBusyException
    Exception class that is thrown when a device is currently servicing a droid, but another device has attempted to assign to it
    DroidDeviceMismatchException
    Exception class that is thrown when a device is attemptting to assign itself to a droid of the incorrect type
